A video recording of the arrest showed Garner gasping, 'I can't breathe' during the fatal encounter.

Thousands have protested the grand jury decision around the United States since the announcement of the decision on Wednesday.

Rose did not speak to reporters after the game. He finished with nine points, six assists and four rebounds in the Warriors' 112-102 victory.

'I respect Derrick a lot,' his Bulls team-mate Joakim Noah said. 

